{"tid":960584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【2018又死一個】《監獄風雲》導演林嶺東驚傳死訊","createTime":"2018-12-29T14:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T17:18:47.000Z","uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b8fdab14645d889cbc01e98f59153304b27a6d15","tid":960584,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/photo/bkn-20181229205448359-1229_00862_001_01p.jpg?20181229215222\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181229%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181229205448359-1229_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20181229215222&h=091d6e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n執導「風雲」三部曲（《龍虎風雲》、《監獄風雲》、《學校風雲》）聞名、現年63歲的林嶺東今午驚傳死訊。警方發言人表示，一名63歲林姓男子在馬鞍山西沙路一單位倒斃，由妻子報案，消息指是導演林嶺東。黑箱車在晚上7時許把遺體送走，其太太和兒子亦目送黑箱車離開，鄰居表示昨日仍跟他打招呼，對此感到十分突然。 <br />\n<br />\n林嶺東擅長拍動作電影，曾以《龍虎風雲》奪得香港電影金像獎最佳導演。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/mobile/bkn-20181229205448359-1229_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181229%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181229205448359-1229_00862_001.html&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bd806a24\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/mobile/bkn-20181229205448359-1229_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7e1e2a96b4907f96dd63e630707b15cbcad6592a","tid":960584,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb3c640e9612f285f5986aa1ba75064f4450e66","tid":960584,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"肥媽 - 友誼之光<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oIGMx5C0KJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoIGMx5C0KJs&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=52da80f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oIGMx5C0KJs</a>"},{"pid":"ebdcebbad3af20c447c16e429f2d4feb8348f374","tid":960584,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"奶共報應再現"},{"pid":"d5daaafc055358ad9e52bc3f4145ae43e6b88dbd","tid":960584,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"out晒啦佢"},{"pid":"81f0907904a2ffd3e05a4fa997c4c14ec3cd2de7","tid":960584,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebdcebbad3af20c447c16e429f2d4feb8348f374","tid":960584,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"奶共報應再現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23868bba2e26fe69dadded94e320f56afb5e6f04","tid":960584,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"肥媽 - 要爭取快樂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZ5fk5cWMlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqZ5fk5cWMlA&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=46be5f74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZ5fk5cWMlA</a>"},{"pid":"d4e10787f50ed55d824d1a653f72e31a6a13cbdc","tid":960584,"uid":47132,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:13:00.000Z","msg":"比時代淘汰既過氣導演"},{"pid":"e145a7400245eafd08ceaaebb6b978f4dd98b5f6","tid":960584,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"天氣凍"},{"pid":"950613eaf6ea5a09bec058b99bd388c77c6d7f47","tid":960584,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"2e161cd3b51703633ce5f9e6cbb5ad4271d01d84","tid":960584,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebdcebbad3af20c447c16e429f2d4feb8348f374","tid":960584,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"奶共報應再現"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"咁你幾時有報應"},{"pid":"4f5e2c85805e059162f1ad3d7f70de02a0530e9a","tid":960584,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:23:23.000Z","msg":"《監獄風雲》導演林嶺東家中猝死<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181229/large/1546092350_eb2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181229%2Flarge%2F1546092350_eb2b.jpg&h=5ed8ca26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n80年代《風雲》系列著名導演林嶺東家中猝死。下午4時許，馬鞍山帝琴灣凱琴居一名女子報案，指其63歲姓林丈夫倒卧床。救護員接報到場，證實林已氣絕身亡。警方經初步調查，相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。消息稱，死者是導演林嶺東。<br />\n<br />\n林嶺東於74年與周潤發、任達華等畢業於第三屆無綫電視藝員訓練班，曾執演過多齣著名電影，包括83年的《陰陽錯》及87年的《龍虎風雲》和《監獄風雲》，當時有《風雲》系列導演之稱，其後闖荷李活拍港產片《目露凶光》、《高度戒備》等，近年已久未在港拍戲，直至去年再與徐克及杜琪峰聯合執導《鐵三角》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181229/59084809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181229%2F59084809&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=65256fba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181229%2F59084809&h=d440db62\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181229/59084809</a>"},{"pid":"531d4182739226e95140ac3f4f24ab8c7de4725f","tid":960584,"uid":86383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"希望係2018最後一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120b8775be6018ffa87b81137122fbbe4bd864ea","tid":960584,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900f433bfcde6a24700360c4cd38819306a577fb","tid":960584,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"拍戲幾好睇<br />\n安息🙏"},{"pid":"b7ef00a0fdecda5e6566ec81c47483c1ee5bb113","tid":960584,"uid":47132,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"2e161cd3b51703633ce5f9e6cbb5ad4271d01d84","tid":960584,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebdcebbad3af20c447c16e429f2d4feb8348f374","tid":960584,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"奶共報應再現"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"咁你幾時有報應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"杜琪峰都有份奶共 幾時到佢<br />\n佢奶共奶到黑社會3都唔拍 應該好快現眼報"},{"pid":"7ba88050087989ac7ca287f7e3309ac20d0cac03","tid":960584,"uid":48582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"900f433bfcde6a24700360c4cd38819306a577fb","tid":960584,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"拍戲幾好睇<br />\n安息🙏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"迷城<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沖天火<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d713026d26e87cf49ba696161aafb0c820b71b","tid":960584,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"肥媽 - 同志！世界在你手！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BJLpPt1cbWw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBJLpPt1cbWw&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ff5c2326\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BJLpPt1cbWw</a>"},{"pid":"d61b33b13bd83f5825ffd1ff8530a5afe9ef190a","tid":960584,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"林嶺東倒斃家中　張耀揚聞噩耗爆喊<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/photo/bkn-20181229220523020-1229_00862_001_01p.jpg?20181229223309\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181229%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181229220523020-1229_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20181229223309&h=c5281979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n導演林嶺東倒斃家中，藝人張耀揚當年獲林嶺東力捧，當年的《龍虎風雲》、《監獄風雲》及《學校風雲》令他打響知名度，近年移居澳門的張耀揚收到消息時感到十分愕然，聞訊後即激動爆喊，一度不能開聲！他坦言：「吓！唔係啩？！我希望呢件事唔係真......（對上一次見佢幾時？）兩年前喺杜琪峯飯局......佢一手捧我出嚟，呢樣嘢一世都會記住，我成日想搵機會報答東San（林嶺東暱稱），但未搵到機會。」他表示會冷靜情緒，着記者稍後再致電給他。<br />\n<br />\n據知，警方接獲林嶺東妻子報案，其妻發現林嶺東倒臥床上，警員到場後，證實林嶺東死亡，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，林嶺東死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/bkn-20181229220523020-1229_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181229%2Fbkn-20181229220523020-1229_00862_001.html&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=66590a92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181229/bkn-20181229220523020-1229_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0aec7477be70d13852cabc8c93da995d2988c548","tid":960584,"uid":86383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2265668/org/a55f760b8161cb0c6341279e50c3c5ab.jpg/dz6ji1Tstd26fOoKDSkDBe2JErPZ3zcgkTwYqZE8GKk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2265668%2Forg%2Fa55f760b8161cb0c6341279e50c3c5ab.jpg%2Fdz6ji1Tstd26fOoKDSkDBe2JErPZ3zcgkTwYqZE8GKk&h=636f94a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea4fadaf2d92372e355f7a01b4459f1a98501f37","tid":960584,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"今年又多個名人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54697773e8b883bdb2af73e867dea8fde3595759","tid":960584,"uid":86383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea4fadaf2d92372e355f7a01b4459f1a98501f37","tid":960584,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"今年又多個名人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"世事多變豈可盡如人意<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ca2f2616fdd7eb29478337963e2590226370d0","tid":960584,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:49:34.000Z","msg":"龍虎風雲 林嶺東導演訪談<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qQdyPvHXwYY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqQdyPvHXwYY&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=db760c95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qQdyPvHXwYY</a>"},{"pid":"3e84a615ee43c497ecc4236eddd54993a10c17f1","tid":960584,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0aec7477be70d13852cabc8c93da995d2988c548","tid":960584,"uid":86383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2265668/org/a55f760b8161cb0c6341279e50c3c5ab.jpg/dz6ji1Tstd26fOoKDSkDBe2JErPZ3zcgkTwYqZE8GKk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2265668%2Forg%2Fa55f760b8161cb0c6341279e50c3c5ab.jpg%2Fdz6ji1Tstd26fOoKDSkDBe2JErPZ3zcgkTwYqZE8GKk&h=636f94a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"做屋邨妹<br />\n畀臭飛玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1f07693ca76de27995e2f9b7c60eb21f367ea8","tid":960584,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"港聞<br />\n2018年12月29日星期六 <br />\n《監獄風雲》導演林嶺東倒斃家中　終年63歲 (22:12)<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181229/s00001/c6e420f4ecccc630fffc2a5caac889ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181229%2Fs00001%2Fc6e420f4ecccc630fffc2a5caac889ba.jpg&h=d0bc04ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今午4時27分，警方接獲一名女子報案，指其63歲姓林丈夫倒卧寓所牀上。救護接報到場，證實林當場死亡，死因有待驗屍後確定，事件無可疑，案件列作「發現屍體」處理。據了解，死者為著名導演林嶺東。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，1955年出生的林嶺東，先是考入無綫電視藝訓班，未幾轉向幕後發展和一度移民外流，1982年回港拍攝首部電影、譚詠麟主演的《陰陽錯》。到1987、88年，林以《龍虎風雲》、《監獄風雲》和《學校風雲》三部曲成為大紅導演，並憑周潤發主演的《龍虎風雲》，拿下第7屆香港電影金像獎最佳導演。<br />\n<br />\n林嶺東其後亦曾拍攝過《高度戒備》等大片，本世紀初曾嘗試到荷里活發展，回流後近作是2007年跟另外兩名著名導演徐克和杜琪峯合作的《鐵三角》、2015年的《迷城》，和2016年的《沖天火》等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181229/s00001/1546092427610/《監獄風雲》導演林嶺東倒斃家中-終年63歲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181229%2Fs00001%2F1546092427610%2F%E3%80%8A%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%B2%E3%80%8B%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E6%9E%97%E5%B6%BA%E6%9D%B1%E5%80%92%E6%96%83%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B463%E6%AD%B2&d=GFPEvlzD3uHCEvk4%2BN4tRghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7a664ec4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181229%2Fs00001%2F1546092427610%2F%E3%80%8A%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%B2%E3%80%8B%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E6%9E%97%E5%B6%BA%E6%9D%B1%E5%80%92%E6%96%83%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B463%E6%AD%B2&h=96009d46\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181229/s00001/1546092427610/《監獄風雲》導演林嶺東倒斃家中-終年63歲</a>"}]}